---
// Selected Work Section
---

<section id="selected-work" class="selected-work">
  <div class="section-layout">
    <div class="section-sidebar">
      <div class="sticky-title fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="section-title">Selected Work</h2>
        <p>在模型边界与真实价值之间</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="work-grid">
        <article class="work-item fade-in-up" data-tone="work-research">
          <div class="image-wrapper bg-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>重新理解语言生成</h3>
            <p>Discrete Flow Matching Language Model (UCLA). 探索不依赖传统自回归范式的语言生成路径。</p>
            <div class="hood-details hidden" data-hood>
              <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Coupling strategy efficiency.</p>
              <p><strong>Method:</strong> Optimizing target distributions for smoother flow.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-item fade-in-up" data-tone="work-product">
          <div class="image-wrapper bg-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>让照片被自然找回</h3>
            <p>AI-Native Photo Album. 基于 CLIP 和自然语言搜索的下一代相册体验。</p>
            <div class="hood-details hidden" data-hood>
              <p><strong>Trade-off:</strong> Latency vs. Embedding precision.</p>
              <p><strong>Constraint:</strong> Client-side storage limitations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-item fade-in-up" data-tone="work-systems">
          <div class="image-wrapper bg-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>让先进模型走向可用</h3>
            <p>并行视频采样与流匹配加速 (ZJU). 解决生成模型的工程化与成本瓶颈。</p>
            <div class="hood-details hidden" data-hood>
              <p><strong>Focus:</strong> Inference speed optimization without degrading FID.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="work-item fade-in-up" data-tone="work-benchmark">
          <div class="image-wrapper bg-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>建立可靠评估方式</h3>
            <p>Continual Learning of Agent Benchmark (NUS). 定义如何测量智能体的持续进化能力。</p>
            <div class="hood-details hidden" data-hood>
              <p><strong>Framework:</strong> Multi-environment sequential tasks avoiding catastrophic forgetting.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="work-postscript fade-in-up" data-tone="postscript">
        <div class="postscript-shell">
          <div class="postscript-meta">
            <p class="label">Postscript</p>
            <p class="postscript-series">失败博物馆 01</p>
          </div>

          <div class="postscript-note">
            <h3>有些失败不该被藏起来，它更像精选案例后的脚注。</h3>
            <p>
              我曾尝试做一个校园外卖拼单产品。最初以为难点会是需求匹配算法与高并发，后来才意识到，真正让它无法成立的，是信任建立、支付清算，以及供给侧冷启动这三个更底层的问题。
            </p>
            <p>
              这件事之后，我开始更警惕“把可实现误判成可成立”。真实世界里，决定产品能不能活下来的，往往不是功能是否做出来，而是用户为什么会信、会用、会留下来。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .selected-work {
    display: block;
  }

  .section-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .section-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .sticky-title {
      position: sticky;
      top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-xl));
    }
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .section-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .work-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .work-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
    align-content: start;
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    transition: transform var(--transition-bounce);
  }

  .work-item:hover .image-wrapper {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
  }

  .caption {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .caption h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--tone-strong);
  }

  .caption p {
    color: var(--tone-muted);
  }

  .hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  :global(body[data-view="detail"]) .hood-details {
    display: block;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--tone-border);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--tone-muted);
  }

  .postscript-shell {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding-top: var(--space-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--tone-border) 85%, transparent);
  }

  .postscript-meta {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .postscript-shell .label,
  .postscript-shell .postscript-series,
  .postscript-shell .postscript-note h3 {
    color: var(--tone-strong);
  }

  .postscript-series {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tone-muted);
  }

  .postscript-note {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding-left: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .postscript-note::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.3rem;
    bottom: 0.3rem;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--tone-solid) 70%, transparent),
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--tone-border) 85%, transparent)
    );
  }

  .postscript-note h3 {
    max-width: 28ch;
    font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 1.8vw, 1.8rem);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .postscript-note p {
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .work-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .postscript-shell {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(9rem, 12rem) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .postscript-note {
      padding-left: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
